measurements.description:
Ten flowers on two 41-cm inflorescences;
	 sepals green overlaid bronze;
	 petals green overlaid bronze, intense burgundy marking proximal three-fourths, widest at base, narrowing along petal;
	 lip white, short burgundy stripe center vein distally, additional burgundy marks each side of stripe;
	 column green, anther cap white;
	 substance medium-firm; texture matte.
